trans-unit.source: The <see cref="N:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions" /> namespace provides classes that enable you to filter data in a Web page by using the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender" /> control.
trans-unit.target: O namespace <see cref="N:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions" /> fornece classes que permitem filtrar dados em uma página da Web usando o controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender" />.

trans-unit.source: This namespace contains expressions that are used with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender> control to filter data in a Web page using declarative syntax.
trans-unit.target: Este namespace contém expressões que são usadas com o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender> controle para filtrar dados em uma página da Web usando a sintaxe declarativa.

trans-unit.source: The classes in this namespace include <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.SearchExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.RangeExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.PropertyExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.OrderByExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.CustomExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: As classes nesse namespace incluem <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.SearchExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.RangeExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.PropertyExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.OrderByExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType> e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.CustomExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
